809
00:38:19,230 --> 00:38:22,290
Are you willing to take a vow in public?

810
00:38:23,250 --> 00:38:24,280
I'm Mo Xiao.

811
00:38:24,890 --> 00:38:27,660
I hereby swear before the gods of the three realms.

812
00:38:27,660 --> 00:38:29,000
From this day forth,

813
00:38:29,400 --> 00:38:31,200
I shall walk the righteous path,

814
00:38:31,260 --> 00:38:32,860
strengthen my Taoist heart,

815
00:38:32,980 --> 00:38:34,480
subdue demons and evil,

816
00:38:34,780 --> 00:38:36,110
and protect all beings.

817
00:38:41,840 --> 00:38:43,170
The Heart Guarding Sand

818
00:38:43,630 --> 00:38:48,040
is the vow each Shushan Sect Leader makes to the world.

819
00:38:48,240 --> 00:38:49,880
Once it is planted

820
00:38:50,830 --> 00:38:51,910
your heart

821
00:38:52,720 --> 00:38:53,610
becomes

822
00:38:54,340 --> 00:38:56,270
the heart of the immortal sects.

823
00:38:56,840 --> 00:39:00,560
All worldly love is cut off from that moment on.

824
00:39:01,740 --> 00:39:03,540
If your heart remains pure,

825
00:39:03,570 --> 00:39:06,210
the Heart Guarding Sand will protect your meridians.

826
00:39:06,210 --> 00:39:08,060
If you harbor thoughts of love,

827
00:39:08,080 --> 00:39:10,610
the Heart Guarding Sand destroys your heart.

828
00:39:11,620 --> 00:39:12,300
Mo Xiao.

829
00:39:13,050 --> 00:39:14,830
Are you willing to accept this?

830
00:39:15,840 --> 00:39:16,560
I

831
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:19,480
am willing.

832
00:39:44,520 --> 00:39:46,040
Heart Guarding Sand.

833
00:39:46,070 --> 00:39:47,530
Isn't that a bit too cruel?

834
00:39:48,060 --> 00:39:49,990
All that,

835
00:39:50,010 --> 00:39:52,140
just to sit in such a joyless position?

836
00:39:52,940 --> 00:39:54,000
The Heart Guarding Sand

837
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:56,400
is like a ruler buried in the body.

838
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:59,080
It's a constant reminder that a Sect Leader

839
00:39:59,080 --> 00:40:00,640
must live only for the world

840
00:40:00,660 --> 00:40:02,310
and the great path of humanity.

841
00:40:02,310 --> 00:40:04,170
He can no longer live for himself.

842
00:40:04,990 --> 00:40:07,160
Will he still remember Feng...

843
00:40:08,230 --> 00:40:09,690
Will he still remember us?

844
00:40:09,810 --> 00:40:11,710
The Heart Guarding Sand guards the Taoist heart.

845
00:40:11,710 --> 00:40:13,130
It cuts off romantic love.

846
00:40:13,130 --> 00:40:14,790
It's not a mind-erasing pill.

847
00:40:15,380 --> 00:40:16,380
That's good then.

848
00:40:17,340 --> 00:40:18,480
As long as he's still my brother,

849
00:40:18,480 --> 00:40:19,940
it doesn't matter whether

850
00:40:20,470 --> 00:40:22,360
he's the Sect Leader or not.
